ROM Info
	lsblk ‚Üí Displays information about block devices (disks, partitions, LVM, etc.) in a tree-like format.
	blkid ‚Üí Show block device attributes
	df -h ‚Üí Disk space usage
	df --block-size=1G ‚Üí Show sizes in GB
